---
title: Lobster Ravioli & Shrimp in a Tomato Cream Sauce
description: Tender ravioli are pretty much great in any form, but they’re especially great when packed with fresh lobster and pillowy ricotta. Add succulent, seared shrimp to the mix and it’s a crustacean celebration! This divine gourmet dish is taken to the next level with a creamy, pink-hued tomato sauce, golden crispy breadcrumbs, and a sprinkle of fresh lemon zest. Be still, our pasta-loving hearts…
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lobster-ravioli-and-shrimp-2042af03.jpg
